NOT... but at least i was headbangin it out to some rufio... but yeh after that i watched simpsons and wrote some songs and i made a website for my cocoa band. i really wanna move somewhere... either cocoa or chicago. i have a craving for some sea world i wannna go so bad i need tickets...hopefully ill score some tonight :P but yeh i REALLY wanna go to a concert soon ANYONE WANNA GO?!?!?! ok well im gonna go drink myself right now and wait for mallo to get home from drumline l8rs :P
